  </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-48aae681-5bdf-4fba-aa2b-e64fc4672c94\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-48aae681-5bdf-4fba-aa2b-e64fc4672c94\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjFfNDQg/MDAxNjUwNTExMjI3Mzkz.YBlWnAeApOhZ5h7mzKp5De48LgooHxh8OA1wwqFyUQog.YaRqlTQtD9fNnWtCWihigNPDgmMB7rLRfo2-TMU_nCAg.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%EC%98%A5%EA%B3%A0_%EC%8A%A4%ED%8B%B1.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2465\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2503\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjFfNDQg/MDAxNjUwNTExMjI3Mzkz.YBlWnAeApOhZ5h7mzKp5De48LgooHxh8OA1wwqFyUQog.YaRqlTQtD9fNnWtCWihigNPDgmMB7rLRfo2-TMU_nCAg.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%EC%98%A5%EA%B3%A0_%EC%8A%A4%ED%8B%B1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjA0MjFfNDQg/MDAxNjUwNTExMjI3Mzkz.YBlWnAeApOhZ5h7mzKp5De48LgooHxh8OA1wwqFyUQog.YaRqlTQtD9fNnWtCWihigNPDgmMB7rLRfo2-TMU_nCAg.JPEG.isuhani/%EA%B2%BD%EC%98%A5%EA%B3%A0_%EC%8A%A4%ED%8B%B1.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"507\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6cc544c-a218-4693-aa2b-9d2c144714e4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E5EF8BE0-11F4-4A1C-96DE-D41E97A3D3D1\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2733AA51-E927-426D-A2BB-CBBE2972280E\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:#333333;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-582C2615-7FD5-4E00-8CEE-CAF899142806\">정(精)과 수(髓)를 보충하고 원기를 북돋우며 혈액을 풍부하게 하여 늙는 것을 막고 몸을 튼튼하게 하며 허로(虛勞)로 머리털이 일찍 희어지고 이가 흔들리며 쉽게 피곤해지는 데 쓴다. 소모성 질병 때 보약으로 쓸 수 있다.</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-62124DC5-29B5-4DA1-B82A-907FFE888F25\"> (한의학대사전, 2001. 6. 15., 한의학대사전 편찬위원회)</span><span style=\"color:#333333;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5DB53680-6FC8-4D90-BFB2-8DC6182EBB05\">&quot;라고 경옥고의 효능이 적혀있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-BC02B20E-9F1F-48FC-9D85-7C4CFA5EBB65\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-2E86B805-3B36-4624-9441-4AF74CDC1E61\">이렇듯 허약해졌거나, 소모성 질병 후 보약으로 쓰이는 경우가 많은데요,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E151554C-6F57-403E-AB03-887041C6DE30\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-9AA48990-F67C-4ED4-B910-97236328F0F7\">특히 경옥고는 폐, 기관지의 기능을 회복하는 효능이 좋아 이전부터 소아, 청소년들의 비염 천식에 노인들의 입마름 및 마른 기침 등에 처방이 많이 되었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2BDF5422-D106-4C43-8DFF-41BBF15E1638\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-8FFD3634-9535-4BC3-8FFC-17E46C84A124\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B749E1A9-1E35-4EFF-9215-92DAF581F2CE\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-BA3DB78A-CE02-4FBD-80C0-9DB045596894\">그렇기에 롱코비드에도 경옥고가 좋은 효과를 보여줍니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-580BAAD0-9956-40C2-9FA3-026B224B0F3C\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs11 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-CC90AD81-73AA-427D-A5EA-5281E9863D6A\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8BA20DF9-8A9B-475E-B3C1-254FBB61A72B\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8369F6E9-B818-46D2-B63A-35F77D8D06B0\">이수한의원에는 복용이 편리한 &#x27;짜먹는 형태의 경옥고스틱&#x27; 도 준비되어 있으니 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B87A19ED-30A4-481B-BE5C-C60B63C6A938\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-AC1F9575-1FB1-4DF0-B132-1494DEC9E80B\">롱코비드로 고생중인 분은 이수한의원에서 치료받으세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7E6516F1-DF82-4798-80C9-8CF443881700\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1A72C987-6BCC-4481-803C-C8064836423E\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-65303344-77F6-4404-8CEA-8A66B4A4E94D\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-968A7B59-2C31-4FB2-9152-2FF3BC8B8521\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-29B82BC7-3CBD-4325-B685-4A15F111B119\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-CBD7816E-2363-4B17-AD17-AA